            <h3 class="highlight-text__header"> Work together, better </h3> 
            <p class="highlight-text__subheader"> Keep your business connected from anywhere with chat and cloud collaboration tools </p> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
          <div class="highlight-image__container float-right"> 
